<h1>Due Diligence Checklist</h1>

<h2>Title & Legal</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Title review</li>
    <li>Rights of way</li>
    <li>Restrictive covenants</li>
</ul>

<h2>Planning</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Existing permissions</li>
    <li>Policy alignment</li>
    <li>Constraints</li>
</ul>

<h2>Physical</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Topography</li>
    <li>Access</li>
    <li>Utilities</li>
</ul>

<h2>Environmental</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Flood risk</li>
    <li>Contamination</li>
    <li>Ecology</li>
</ul>

<h2>Commercial</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Market context</li>
    <li>Comparable evidence</li>
    <li>Viability indicators</li>
</ul>
